        "created_at": "2019-11-27T00:11:27.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Taking this tomorrow to a special dinner. I have zero experience with CdP and want the wine to show well.</p>\n<p>Besides pairing it with Sushi how would you approach this wine in regards to decanting? I\u2019ve checked cellartracker and I am aware of the high proportion of flawed bottles so I will bring a back up.</p>\n<p>Thanks for the help!</p>",
