        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/49beb7/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-11-27T18:56:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I really did not care for this wine the last time I had it. Over the top on the ripe side. An 06 recently was much better. Decant as long as possible (at cellar temp ideally) and bring a back up bottle would be my advice.</p>\n<p>Tom</p>",
