        "created_at": "2019-11-27T18:59:35.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This wine is a special case, as it re-fermented in bottle and produced lots of gas! So decant aggressively for an hour or two to let it de-gas. And tell me how it is, as I haven\u2019t tried a bottle for a handful of years.</p>",
